Load necessary libraries
```{r}
library(dplyr)
```


Read in the data
```{r}
df <- read.csv("TechSurvey - Survey.csv")
```

Look at summary statistics
```{r}
summary(df)
```

Remove values for other response variables
```{r}
df <- df %>% select(-c(PG5_1RRPQ,PG5_8CP,PG5_3HDS,PG5_4VGP,PG5_7NDYP,PG5_13NFG,PG5_9FRP,
                       PG5_6SSYOP,PG5_10RPA,PG5_2BNUI,PG5_11NSG,PG5_12NWG))
```
